  "doc_id": "14653",
  "text": "The Bag-of-Colors (BoC) model proposed in [CITATION_1] uses RGB values of each pixel as the color descriptor, while some work proves that region-based local color features are effective for person re-identification [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . We divide the image into rectangular blocks and extract region-based color features including root Color Histogram and Color Names.",
